videos.description: Nate Stanley and Brandon Smith hook up for a 15-yard score for Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hawkeyes score first against Nebraska) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawkeyes score first against Nebraska

videos.description: Jack Stoll catches a short pass and takes it in for a score to tie the game up at 7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cornhuskers' Stoll dives for a TD) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cornhuskers' Stoll dives for a TD

videos.description: Toren Young takes it in for a touchdown from the 4-yard line to give Iowa the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Young cuts and scores untouched) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young cuts and scores untouched

videos.description: Mehki Sargent out runs the Nebraska defense for a touchdown to increase Iowa's lead before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa scores right before halftime) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa scores right before halftime

videos.description: Hawkeyes' Mehki Sargent scores again with a 4-yard touchdown catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa’s Sargent scores his second TD) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa's Sargent scores his second TD

videos.description: Adrian Martinez's touchdown pass cuts Iowa's lead to 28-20 over Nebraska.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Martinez hooks up with Washington for Cornhuskers TD) 2018// ESHEET

videos.headline: Martinez hooks up with Washington for Cornhuskers TD

videos.description: Adrian Martinez scrambles then finds Kade Warner in the back of the end zone for 2-point conversion.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nebraska ties game with 2-point conversion) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nebraska ties game with 2-point conversion

videos.description: Iowa beats Nebraska 31-28 as Miguel Recinos makes the game-winning field goal with 3 seconds left.
